These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Food: avocado, peas, pomegranate, kale
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. Food:avocado is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and Food:peas##2
4. Food:kale is on the far left##1
5. Food:pomegranate is between Food:peas and Food:avocado##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | kale         | peas   | pomegranate | avocado       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Cigar: ritmeester, game, pall-mall, tiparillo
1. Cigar:tiparillo is between Hobby:reading and Cigar:game##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Cigar:pall-mall is on the right of Cigar:ritmeester##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Cigar:ritmeester##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Cigar   | game    | tiparillo   | ritmeester | pall-mall       |

