1. Movie-Genre:epic == Pet:lizard##1
2. Pet:cat is between Movie-Genre:western and Pet:rat##2
3. Movie-Genre:epic is on the far right##1
4. Pet:cat is on the right of Movie-Genre:comedy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | spy | western | epic |

